bug.short_desc: Private/protected items are not displayed correctly after deselection.

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1026 screenshot
Open the API Viewer and search for "__." to get all results for private members.
Now select one private member, the Viewer selects the member blue. When you now select a other private member (from the same class) the previous selected private member gets the wrong color (green) but it should be red.
fixed on branch 1_4_x with rev. 28104 fixed on trunk with rev. 28105
Closed all bugs already shipped with a release.
